Additional Terms for Educational Use:

This software is specifically designed for educational purposes and child safety.
While the MIT license allows commercial use, the authors encourage using this
software primarily for:

1. Educational institutions (schools, libraries, learning centers)
2. Non-profit educational organizations
3. Parents and families for home education
4. Open source educational projects

The authors request that any commercial use maintains the child-safe and
educational focus of the original project.

